79
00:04:34,930 --> 00:04:35,870
Father!

80
00:04:36,110 --> 00:04:36,990
Father!

81
00:04:37,580 --> 00:04:38,700
Father!

82
00:04:39,460 --> 00:04:40,340
Father,

83
