100
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:26,260
In recovering the Qiankun Pearl this time,

101
00:05:26,550 --> 00:05:28,720
King Yan deserves the highest merit.

102
00:05:28,730 --> 00:05:29,860
I was not mistaken.

103
00:05:30,290 --> 00:05:32,740
